# Solo Developer Guidelines — Master Reference

> This file is the single source of truth for solo developer constraints.
> All AI IDEs must read this before writing any code.

## The Solo Developer Philosophy

1. **Start small** — 6 services, not 30
2. **Add complexity when you feel the pain** — not before
3. **One developer, one machine** — everything in Docker Compose
4. **Revenue before polish** — working agents before beautiful code
5. **AI IDE does the heavy lifting** — you focus on architecture decisions

---

## Stage Technology Matrix

This table tells you EXACTLY what to use at each stage. If it says "—" you must NOT use it.

| Technology | Stage 1 | Stage 2 | Stage 3 | Stage 4 |
|-----------|---------|---------|---------|---------|
| **LLM Provider** | Stubbed (RAG chunks) | Ollama + LiteLLM | Ollama + LiteLLM | +vLLM or Groq |
| **Background Tasks** | — | ARQ | ARQ | Celery or Temporal |
| **Message Queue** | — | Redis Streams | Redis Streams | NATS JetStream |
| **Secret Management** | .env files | .env files | Vault | Vault |
| **Auth** | Simple JWT | Simple JWT | Simple JWT | Keycloak + OPA |
| **Web Scraping** | — | httpx | Browserless | +Proxy rotation |
| **Data Modelling** | PostgreSQL | PostgreSQL | PostgreSQL JSONB | +Neo4j |
| **Code Sandbox** | — | — | Docker sandbox | microsandbox |
| **API Gateway** | — | — | — | Traefik |
| **Service Mesh** | — | — | — | Istio (if K8s) |
| **Orchestration** | Docker Compose | Docker Compose | Docker Compose | Docker or K8s |
| **Prompt Injection** | — | — | LLM Guard | LLM Guard |
| **Observability** | Docker logs | Docker logs | Docker logs | OTEL + Grafana |

