## Hardware Requirements

| Stage | Minimum RAM | Recommended | Notes |
|-------|-------------|-------------|-------|
| 1 | 4 GB | 8 GB | Just Docker + 6 services |
| 2 | 8 GB | 16 GB | Ollama loaded models |
| 3 | 16 GB | 32 GB | Browserless uses RAM |
| 4 | 32 GB | 64 GB | Per component added |

---

## When to Move to the Next Stage

### Stage 1 → Stage 2
Move when: Stage 1 complete (all 20 tasks done, v0.1.0 tagged on GitHub)

### Stage 2 → Stage 3
Move when: Stage 2 complete AND Lead Scout is finding real jobs.
The pain: "I found good jobs but can't respond fast enough manually"

### Stage 3 → Stage 4
Move when: Revenue > £0/month AND a specific pain from the trigger list.
Never add Stage 4 services preemptively.

